A simplified Jetpack Joyride-style 2D game built in C++ using SFML and advanced Object-Oriented Programming principles.
Players control a character with a jetpack, fly to avoid obstacles, collect coins, and use power-ups. The goal: survive as long as possible while scoring points ğŸš€.

ğŸ‘¥ Authors
Noam Kazav
